{"tid":791301,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"保安懷疑未夠21歲 黎瑞恩被查證件超級興奮","createTime":"2018-08-23T16:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T05:43:32.000Z","uid":160973,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4c847dc29e1908de0f9ea660b00d6c03b0756bfd","tid":791301,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"二十多年沒有到美國演出的黎瑞恩（小恩子），剛從洛杉磯及內華達州的Reno（雷諾）登台返港，此行的「最大收穫」，是證明了小恩子青春常駐，超級「凍齡」。<br />\n<br />\n兩場演出，歌迷反應熱烈，衝到台前與小恩子握手，隨和的小恩子自然有求必應，一路唱一路握手。<br />\n<br />\n完成Reno的Peppermill賭場劇院演出後，大會安排在酒店的酒廊慶功，發生了一件令小恩子意想不到的趣事。<br />\n<br />\n當小恩子入場時，守在門口的保安竟然把她攔截，要求她出示身份證，原因是懷疑她未夠21歲，早已是一子一女之母的小恩子，面對這美麗的懷疑，興奮得即時飛撲攬着外籍保安，問對方：「你真係查我身份證？」對方一臉嚴肅回答：「係！不夠21歲不可以入場。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2BEbLrX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BEbLrX&d=wCS1pVCWk9FORZ9yatMrfwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6a4fb87d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2BEbLrX</a>"},{"pid":"a8e4862e57f2af707c4a94dbde7770e1796fd78c","tid":791301,"uid":8966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T04:00:24.000Z","msg":"賭場都會查呀叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd3735fc2567409e4fe567f82c49e2814a2a8bb","tid":791301,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:06:59.000Z","msg":"小恩子好鐘意作新聞上報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前夫咁有錢, 無比夠贍養費佢咩<br />\n點解仲要出黎唱, 又要跟家燕媽媽搵食登台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f86c4907568fe8371834dcaebb2a2c5e24ea2b","tid":791301,"uid":60814,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"邊撚個？"},{"pid":"5e4e2da618cf99741ddab1c9e950a594fd8f9945","tid":791301,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c264120b1b7adfcef318a42551491990bf1741","